Metadata.Title: Orden de asesinato: 1-37-0743816-48
Metadata.Description: The mission involves eliminating deserters and traitors from the ninja clan in Hokkaido. Shinobi 47, the last survivor of his clan, has been designated for this task. Now working for the agency, he must employ his stealth and combat skills to neutralize the targets, who have changed their names and faces. The new identities of the objectives are available. Discretion is crucial to the success of the mission, and once completed, the agent will retreat without a trace.
